{"tid":1335400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[時事與數學] 大家記住易賤制function係有兩個方向","createTime":"2019-07-20T13:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T13:59:13.000Z","uid":48234,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d3fa2b7c5b3854bf1daa1c42a091c09c4fbf26a","tid":1335400,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"根據巴打 愛情波函數 嘅結果<br />\nYijinecimal (毅進制):<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Y(<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">x</span>)</span> ~= <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">x^0.8858</span><br />\n<br />\n今日我就同大家講一樣嘢: Inverse function, 逆轉函數<br />\nInverse Yijinecimal (逆毅進制):<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Y^-1(<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">x</span>)</span> ~= <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">x^1.1289</span><br />\n<br />\n今日警賊公佈撐<del>警</del>共遊行人數為10.3萬，有冇人信?<br />\n好簡單，因為警賊用咗<span style=\"color: red;\">逆毅進制</span><br />\n咁點算呀? 用返<span style=\"color: gold;\">毅進制</span>嚟計咪大約估到正確人數囉!<br />\nx = <span style=\"color: gold;\">Y(<span style=\"color: red;\">Y^-1(<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">x</span>)</span>)</span> = <span style=\"color: red;\">Y^-1(<span style=\"color: gold;\">Y(<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">x</span>)</span>)</span><br />\n<br />\nY(103000) = 103000^0.8858 ~= 27566 ~= 27600<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">毅進仔，算撚數啦你哋，你哋想操控民意?<br />\n警賊始終都係唔適合玩政治㗎啦</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf80350a9b9da998b413a1a658a4b5ea88dc1035","tid":1335400,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好以為用逆易賤制，可以呃到香港市民!</span></span>"},{"pid":"ba9dd77f21b1624d398d1549bd6d9e22e1007550","tid":1335400,"uid":4931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"數學家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7f0c2ff31c2c8da053641202024d186063f2d8","tid":1335400,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a84dd4920d2648bbccd528864e15c83f46b914","tid":1335400,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T07:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340a946b1947f4b4dc892b38c8837ffd0fc69dfc","tid":1335400,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}